Belton Regional Medical Center is one of 10 HCA Midwest Health System hospitals in the Kansas City and surrounding areas. Located conveniently at Highways 71 and 58 in Belton, Mo., Belton Regional Medical Center is an 85-bed acute care facility offering a full range of inpatient and outpatient services.




